<BaseLayout title="About">
  <div class="prose max-w-none">
    <h1>About WealthLab</h1>
    <p>
      WealthLab is a blog dedicated to the intersection of <strong>personal finance</strong>
      and <strong>AI-powered tools</strong>. We believe that building wealth in the modern era
      means leveraging the best technology available — from budgeting automations to
      AI-driven investment analysis.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Cover</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Personal Finance Fundamentals</strong> — budgeting, saving, investing, and retirement planning</li>
      <li><strong>AI Tool Reviews</strong> — hands-on reviews of AI tools for finance, productivity, and decision-making</li>
      <li><strong>Automation Strategies</strong> — using technology to put your finances on autopilot</li>
      <li><strong>Market Analysis</strong> — AI-informed perspectives on trends and opportunities</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Why This Blog?</h2>
    <p>
      Most finance advice ignores technology. Most tech content ignores practical money management.
      WealthLab bridges that gap — giving you actionable strategies that combine financial wisdom
      with cutting-edge tools.
    </p>

    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>
      Have a question, suggestion, or want to collaborate? Reach out at
      <a href="mailto:hello@wealthlab.blog">hello@wealthlab.blog</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
